tribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"wordpress themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=233908\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:634:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for wedding and engagement? Then look no further. Here&#8217;s the list of some of the most stylish, fancy, and adorable WordPress themes for wedding and engagement. You can just dive in and start selecting your wedding theme that matches your requirements and then add some plugins to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-wedding-and-engagement/\">23 Best WordPress Themes For Wedding and Engagement (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31989:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for wedding and engagement?</p>\n<p>Then look no further. Here&#8217;s the list of some of the most stylish, fancy, and adorable WordPress themes for wedding and engagement. You can just dive in and start selecting your wedding theme that matches your requirements and then add some plugins to enhance its features. </p>\n<h3>Choosing a WordPress Theme for Wedding and Engagement Website</h3>\n<p>There are thousands of free and premium WordPress themes on the market that let you create a wedding or engagement website. A good WordPress theme for wedding and engagement website must have some features like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Photo and video galleries with lightbox popup</li>\n<li>Support for location maps</li>\n<li>Compatibility with event plugins</li>\n<li>Social sharing icons</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress themes for wedding and engagement.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-theme.jpg\" alt=\"Divi Theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233913\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-theme-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-theme-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Divi</a> is a powerful WordPress theme and page builder by Elegant Themes. Divi is perfect for creating all types of websites, including wedding, engagement, event planning, etc. This theme has built-in layouts, custom post types, and widgetized homepage.</p>\n<p>It offers several color choices, sidebars, background, and support for WooCommerce. Divi is compatible with WPML, so you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a> with ease.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233934\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Ultra</a> is a multi-purpose WordPress theme to build any kind of website. Ultra comes with several design skins and pre-made demo sites. It&#8217;s also shipped with a layout for wedding and engagement sites. With a fullscreen background, you can feature wedding dates, images, videos, and RSVP button.</p>\n<p>The Ultra theme is highly customizable and is bundled with the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-builder/\" title=\"Themify Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Themify builder</a> to help you design your layout quickly and easily. It&#8217;s compatible with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-themes-online-store/\" title=\"50+ Best WooCommerce Themes for Your Online Store\">WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Astra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra.jpg\" alt=\"Astra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233932\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Astra</a> is a modern WordPress theme designed to build lightning fast websites. It comes with tons of demo sites, including one for wedding and engagement. You can also find several built-in header layouts to customize your header the way you want. This theme also comes with a navigation menu, custom logo, and a fullscreen background image.</p>\n<p>Astra is compatible with popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">drag and drop page builders</a>. It&#8217;s a lightweight theme and it needs only less than 50 KB of resources.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-essence-pro/\" title=\"Essence Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Essence Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-essence-pro/\" title=\"Essence Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/essense-pro.jpg\" alt=\"Essence Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233912\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/essense-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/essense-pro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/essense-pro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-essence-pro/\" title=\"Essence Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Essence Pro</a> is a beautiful WordPress theme built on top of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Framework</a>. It&#8217;s highly customizable and supports page builders to make changes on your website. This theme is perfect for the wedding, engagement, and wedding planners&#8217; websites.</p>\n<p>It features a fullscreen background image, navigation menu, search bar, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-newsletter-plugins/\" title=\"11 Best Email Newsletter Plugins for WordPress\">newsletter subscription box</a>, and more. You can also use the WordPress customizer with live preview to edit theme settings.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233933\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">OceanWP</a> is a popular WordPress theme for wedding, engagement, event planners, and more It has beautiful crisp typography, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Slider Plugins\">image slider</a>, navigation menu, and beautiful homepage sections to display your photos. </p>\n<p>The best part is that the core theme is completely free. You can purchase the extension bundle if you&#8217;d like that enhances your website easily. It includes color sc