dSnap is what you need for your website. This theme offers impressive features including fullscreen background image, sidebar navigation menu, homepage sections, and more.</p>\n<p>With WedSnap, you can set up a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a WordPress Blog (&#038; Make Extra Income)\">separate blog page</a> to post articles and share your photography projects. WedSnap has color skins, social icons, custom widgets, and a built-in contact form template for your page.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-vignette/\" title=\"Vignette\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">20. Vignette</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-vignette/\" title=\"Vignette\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/vignette.jpg\" alt=\"Vignette\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233928\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/vignette.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/vignette-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/vignette-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-vignette/\" title=\"Vignette\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Vignette</a> is a WordPress photography theme for wedding, engagement, and event photographers. It has a flexible homepage layout to showcase your photos in a professional style. It also comes with multiple layout options for each of your image galleries.</p>\n<p>Other notable features include custom widgets, a theme options panel, social media integration, and compatibility with Jetpack.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-selfie/\" title=\"Selfie\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">21. Selfie</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/organizedthemes-selfie/\" title=\"Selfie\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selfie.jpg\" alt=\"Selfie\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233929\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selfie.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selfie-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/selfie-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Selfie is another WordPress wedding photography theme. It&#8217;s crafted beautifully with blocks to add image galleries, photos, and content to the homepage. This theme can also be used to display your photography portfolio site.</p>\n<p>It has built-in <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-image-optimization-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"6 Best Image Optimization Plugins for WordPress (Compared)\">lazy loading images</a> feature to speed up your website. Selfie theme supports Google Fonts, custom colors, and image background.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-parallax-pro/\" title=\"Parallax Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">22. Parallax Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-parallax-pro/\" title=\"Parallax Pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/parallax-pro.jpg\" alt=\"Parallax Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233930\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/parallax-pro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/parallax-pro-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/parallax-pro-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Parallax Pro is a visually attractive black and white WordPress theme for all kinds of websites. With Parallax Pro, you can create a website for wedding and engagement planners. This theme is built on top of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" title=\"Genesis Framework\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Genesis Framework</a>, making it robust and reliable.</p>\n<p>It has homepage widget areas to customize the website quickly. Parallax Pro supports eCommerce to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store  Step by Step\">start an online store</a>, which also lets you sell wedding stock photos.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-wedding-planner/\" title=\"Wedding Planner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">23. Wedding Planner</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/inkthemes-wedding-planner/\" title=\"Wedding Planner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wedding-planner.jpg\" alt=\"Wedding Planner\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233931\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wedding-planner.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wedding-planner-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wedding-planner-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Wedding Planner is a stunning WordPress theme for wedding, engagement, and event organizers. It helps you promote your wedding planning business with its <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-content-marketing-tools-plugins-wordpress/\" title=\"15 Best Content Marketing Tools and Plugins for WordPress\">content marketing tools</a> and features. It can integrate your Instagram profile to share photos directly from Instagram.</p>\n<p>This theme ships with multiple blog sections, beautiful gallery design, contact form template, and modern pre-built layouts. Wedding Planner theme is highly optimized for SEO and performance.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress themes for wedding and engagement. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-photography-themes-for-wordpress/\" title=\"43 Best Photography Themes for WordPress\">best photography themes for WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-wedding-and-engagement/\">23 Best WordPress Themes For Wedding and Engagement (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-wedding-and-engagement/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"9 Best PCI Compliant Web Hosting Companies (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pci-compliant-web-hosting/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pci-compliant-web-hosting/#respond\";s:7:\"attri