strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GreenGeeks.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with GreenGeeks &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>GreekGeeks is one of the few PCI compliant shared hosting companies. Aside from PCI compliance, they&#8217;re well-known for being one of the largest eco-friendly hosting providers.</p>\n<p>Aside from PCI compliance, here are a few features of GreenGeeks plans:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A free SSL certificate and dedicated IP address</li>\n<li>Eco-friendly hosting</li>\n<li>Reduced risk of a security breach</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Starts at $9.95 per month. You can getan exclusive discount by using our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/coupons/greengeeks/\" title=\"GreenGeeks\">GreenGeeks coupon</a> code.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/greengeeks-review/\" title=\"GreenGeeks\">Read our GreenGeeks review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/godaddy-wordpress-hosting-review.png\" alt=\"GoDaddy WordPress Hosting Review\" width=\"370\" height=\"220\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221572\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. GoDaddy</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: &#8211; </li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: &#8211; </li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 8/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GoDaddy.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/godaddy-hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with GoDaddy &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>GoDaddy is a budget-friendly web hosting company. All their eCommerce related products are entirely PCI compliant, which means your payments are secure on GoDaddy. However, if your website requires card details from customers, then you need to assess it yourself for PCI compliance.</p>\n<p>With GoDaddy, you&#8217;ll get:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Automatic account setup</li>\n<li>99% uptime guarantee</li>\n<li>Daily website backups</li>\n<li>Automatic WordPress core updates</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> $2.49 per month (70% off). To get the discount, you can check out our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/coupons/godaddy/\" title=\"GoDaddy\">GoDaddy coupon</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/godaddy-review/\" title=\"GoDaddy\">Read our complete GoDaddy review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/liquidweb-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/liquid-web-woocommerce-hosting-review.png\" alt=\"Liquid Web WooCommerce Hosting Review\" width=\"370\" height=\"227\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-221572\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/liquidweb-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Liquid Web WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 901 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.99%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/liquidweb-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">LiquidWeb.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/liquidweb-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with Liquid Web &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Liquid Web WooCommerce hosting offers a perfect platform to host your online store. Their customer support team will help you in getting a PCI Compliance certification for your website and create a secure environment for online payments.</p>\n<p>Liquid Web WooCommerce hosting