re features on your online store</li>\n<li>VaultPress compatibility to create secure off-site backups</li>\n<li>Auto updates for WordPress core, themes, and plugins</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> $24.95 per month (Usually $29.95 / mo.). Check out our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/coupons/dreamhost/\" title=\"DreamHost\">DreamHost coupon</a> to get discounted price.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/dreamhost-review/\">Read our DreamHost review &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article has helped you find the best PCI compliant web hosting companies to host your website. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/ecommerce/\" title=\"Best eCommerce Hosting Companies (Real Reviews)\">best eCommerce hosting companies</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/pci-compliant-web-hosting/\">9 Best PCI Compliant Web Hosting Companies (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://www.isitwp.com/pci-compliant-web-hosting/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"How to Hire a Professi