1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:656:\"<p>Are you looking for the best 24/7 WordPress support services? WordPress support and maintenance services help you manage your websites, such as monitoring and updating WordPress core, themes, and plugins, backups, performance optimization, etc. In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best 24/7 WordPress support services that you can use to manage your website. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-support-services/\">10 Best 24/7 WordPress Support Services to Manage Your Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14606:\"<p>Are you looking for the best 24/7 WordPress support services?</p>\n<p>WordPress support and maintenance services help you manage your websites, such as monitoring and updating WordPress core, themes, and plugins, backups, performance optimization, etc. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best 24/7 WordPress support services that you can use to manage your website.</p>\n<h3>Why Do You Need WordPress Support Services?</h3>\n<p>Maintaining a WordPress website can be a daunting task, especially if you&#8217;re not a tech-savvy person. Even if you have the right technical skill, you might not want to allocate an hour every day to manage your WordPress site. Instead of maintaining WordPress, you can focus on producing great content and growing your online business. </p>\n<p>Here&#8217;re a few things a WordPress support service can help you with. </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Security</strong>: Protect your websites from hackers and malware.</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime monitoring</strong>: Keep your WordPress site up and running all the time.</li>\n<li><strong>Performance</strong>: Optimize your website for speed and performance.</li>\n<li><strong>Analytics</strong>: Monitor your website traffic and gather actionable insights.</li>\n<li><strong>Update</strong>: Update your WordPress core, themes, and plugins without breaking your site.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Every WordPress support service is unique. Before you <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hire-a-professional-wordpress-developer/\" title=\"How to Hire a Professional WordPress Developer (8 Places)\">hire a professional developer</a> or WordPress support service, double check if they provide the right services for your needs. </p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best 24/7 WordPress support services available.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpbuffs/\" title=\"WP Buffs\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. WP Buffs</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpbuffs/\" title=\"WP Buffs\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpbuffs-1.jpg\" alt=\"WP Buffs\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233850\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpbuffs-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpbuffs-1-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpbuffs-1-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Buffs is a popular 24/7 WordPress maintenance and management support service. It has a remote team that works 24/7 to help you tackle any of your website issues. Their service gives you access to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ithemes-security/\" title=\"iThemes Security\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">iThemes Security Pro</a>, the best WordPress security plugin.</p>\n<p>This service also recommends using <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-rocket/\" title=\"WP Rocket\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">WP Rocket</a> for speed optimization. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.fixrunner.com/\" title=\"Fixrunner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. FixRunner</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.fixrunner.com/\" title=\"FixRunner\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixrunner.jpg\" alt=\"FixRunner\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233851\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixrunner.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixrunner-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixrunner-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>FixRunner is an affordable WordPress help and support service. Aside from monitoring and maintenance, you can rely on FixRunner even if it&#8217;s a quick fix or a development task. They also manage your WordPress updates for themes and plugins.</p>\n<p>Their website monitoring team makes sure that your site is up and running 24/7, so you can have peace of mind. They also provide you with a cloud backup service to store backups and restore your website within minutes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.wpsitecare.com/\" title=\"WP Site Care\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. WP Site Care</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wpsitecare.com/\" title=\"WP Site Care\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-site-care.jpg\" alt=\"WP Site Care\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233852\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-site-care.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-site-care-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-site-care-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Site Care is a WordPress support and maintenance service. Their team makes sure that your website runs fast and secure. It monitors your website 24/7 to give you peace of mind, so you can focus on growing your business instead of spending your time on server administration tasks.</p>\n<p>With automated backups, your website&#8217;s database, files, and images are stored offsite in the cloud. WP Site Care also optimizes the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/boost-wordpress-performance-speed/\" title=\"How to Boost WordPress Performance &#038; Speed (Expert Advice)\">performance of your website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wp-techsupport.com/\" title=\"WP Tech Support\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. WP Tech Support</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wp-techsupport.com/\" title=\"WP Tech Support\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-tech-support.jpg\" alt=\"WP Tech Support\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233853\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-tech-support.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-tech-support-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wp-tech-support-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Tech Support is a WordPress help and support service. If your site is facing any issue, then you can submit a request and their support team will help you solve it. </p>\n<p>You can use their online customer support portal to access your reports and connect with the support team. It covers all necessary services like website monitoring, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-backup-plugins-compared/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Backup Plugins\">backups</a>, updates, and performance optimization.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpsiteplan.com/\" title=\"WP SitePlan\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. WP SitePlan</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpsiteplan.com/\" title=\"WP SitePlan\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpsiteplan.jpg\" alt=\"WP SitePlan\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233845\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpsiteplan.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpsiteplan-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpsiteplan-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP SitePlan offers WordPress maintenance service and support plans. It provides security solutions to protect your website from hackers and malware. Other services include bug fixing and monitoring of your website. It optimizes the database ensuring your site runs without errors.</p>\n<p>You can rely on WP SitePlan for uptime monitoring, tracking analytics, and installing updates smoothly. They also give support for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-woocommerce-themes-online-store/\" title=\"50+ Best WooCommerce Themes for Your Online Store\">WooCommerce</a> stores.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpcurve.com/\" title=\"WP Curve\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. WP Curve</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpcurve.com/\" title=\"WP Curve\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpcurve.jpg\" alt=\"WP Curve\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233844\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpcurve.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpcurve-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpcurve-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Curve is a premium WordPress support service. Their team of WordPress experts and developers work 24/7 to solve your website issues. Some of their notable services include website security, speed optimization, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/\" title=\"9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!\">driving traffic</a>, and reducing your bounce rate.</p>\n<p>You can submit any assignments like bug fixing, website development, updates, etc. and they will complete the task in a specified amount of time. They also offer a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\" title=\"14 Best Live Chat Software Plugins\">live chat</a> facility to connect with their team.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://maintainn.com/\" title=\"Maintainn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Maintainn</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://maintainn.com/\" title=\"Maintainn\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/maintainn.jpg\" alt=\"Maintainn\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233846\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/maintainn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/maintainn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/maintainn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Maintainn is a WordPress support and maintenance service. It provides design, development, and maintenance solutions for WordPress websites. It&#8217;s integrated with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Sucuri</a> to provide world-class security and 24/7 monitoring of your site.</p>\n<p>Other significant features include updates for WordPress core, themes, and plugins. With Maintainn, you can create offsite backups and restore quickly without losing any data.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordx.press/\" title=\"WordXpress\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. WordXpress</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordx.press/\" title=\"WordXpress\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wordxpress.jpg\" alt=\"WordXpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233847\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wordxpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wordxpress-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wordxpress-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WordXpress is excellent support, maintenance, and marketing solution for WordPress. It includes regular updates, offsite cloud backups, and malware scanning. It also provides unlimited edits, fixes, and changes for your WordPress website. You can use this service for page speed monitoring, spam protection, and more.</p>\n<p>With WordXpress, you&#8217;ll get a modern <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">page builder</a>, access to SendGrid email tool, and Google Analytics support. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpmaintainer.com/\" title=\"WP Maintainer\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. WP Maintainer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpmaintainer.com/\" title=\"WP Maintainer\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpmaintainer.jpg\" alt=\"WP Maintainer\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233848\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpmaintainer.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpmaintainer-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wpmaintainer-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Maintainer is a WordPress update, backups, and maintenance support solution. It works with Sucuri to create a security layer and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/ultimate-wordpress-security-guide-beginner-friendly/\" title=\"The Complete WordPress Security Guide (Beginner Friendly)\">protect your website</a> from hackers, malicious content, and malware. </p>\n<p>It offers smooth updates for latest WordPress version, theme, and plugins of your website. You can also schedule site backups, email them, or download on your computer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://fixmysite.com/\" title=\"Fixmysite.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Fixmysite.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://fixmysite.com/\" title=\"Fixmysite.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixmysite.jpg\" alt=\"Fixmysite\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233849\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixmysite.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixmysite-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/fixmysite-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Fixmysite can help you fix your WordPress website right away. It works in 3 simple steps: contact, review, and fix. They offer theme customization, migration, speed optimization, and malware removal from your WordPress website.</p>\n<p>You can connect with them for a site audit and even for a WordPress setup.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best 24/7 WordPress support services to manage your site. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-help-desk-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Help Desk Plugins for Customer Support\">best WordPress help desk plugins for customer support</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-support-services/\">10 Best 24/7 WordPress Support Services to Manage Your Site</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-support-services/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"11 Best QuickBooks Alternatives for Small Businesses (2019)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://www.isitwp.com/quickbooks-alternatives/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/quickbooks-alternatives/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 26 Jun 2019 10:37:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"accounting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"quickbooks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"quickbooks alternatives\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"wordpress software\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=233669\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:630:\"<p>Are you looking for the best QuickBooks alternatives? While QuickBooks is the smartest business tools provider for your income and billing management, it may lack a few features that could help organize your accounts accurately. In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best QuickBooks alternatives that you can use to manage your books and [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/quickbooks-alternatives/\">11 Best QuickBooks Alternatives for Small Businesses (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15391:\"<p>Are you looking for the best QuickBooks alternatives?</p>\n<p>While QuickBooks is the smartest business tools provider for your income and billing management, it may lack a few features that could help organize your accounts accurately.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best QuickBooks alternatives that you can use to manage your books and accounts.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshbooks/\" title=\"FreshBooks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. FreshBooks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/freshbooks/\" title=\"FreshBooks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freshbooks.jpg\" alt=\"FreshBooks\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233689\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freshbooks.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freshbooks-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freshbooks-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>FreshBooks is one of the most popular invoice and billing software. It helps you create professional and custom invoices with your logo, background, etc. It allows you to accept credit card payments on your invoices and support multiple payment integrations.</p>\n<p>It comes with many other services like time tracking, expense tracking, projects management, and estimates/proposals. You can generate powerful insights and reports about the performance of your business.</p>\n<p>Other prominent features include automatic tax calculation, invoice due dates, payment notifications, and more. You can choose your preferred currency and also give discounts to your users. FreshBooks is a perfect alternative to QuickBooks.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starter plan costs $15 / month. This plan is perfect for 5 billable clients. If you want to try their service before purchasing, you can also sign up for the free trial.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.zoho.com/books\" title=\"Zoho Books\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Zoho Books</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zoho.com/books\" title=\"Zoho Books\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zoho-books.jpg\" alt=\"Zoho Books\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233690\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zoho-books.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zoho-books-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zoho-books-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Zoho Books is a simple and secure online accounting solution for your business. It connects with your bank account to manage the flow of your payments, track payments, and categorize the transactions smartly. They provide you with a portal to accept bulk payments, share recent sales, gather customer feedback, and more.</p>\n<p>It also manages and tracks your inventory and can be integrated with multiple services for payments, analytics, reporting, and CRM. </p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $9 / month per organization. You can sign up for their 14-days free trial to check the service before you purchase it.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.xero.com/\" title=\"Xero\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Xero</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.xero.com/\" title=\"Xero\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/xero.jpg\" alt=\"Xero\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233691\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/xero.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/xero-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/xero-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Xero is an excellent business and accounting software for small businesses. It gives a real-time view of your cash flow on all devices. It has a mobile app that comes in handy to send invoices, create expense claims, and more.</p>\n<p>It categorizes your transactions and generates statements quickly. Xero supports multiple currencies, integrates with over 700 apps, and create purchase orders on the go.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It offers a 30-day free trial to try their service risk-free. The starter package costs $20 per month for up to 5 invoices and quotes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.sage.com/en-gb/shop/sage50c/\" title=\"Sage 50Cloud\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Sage 50Cloud</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sage.com/en-gb/shop/sage50c/\" title=\"Sage 50Cloud\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sage-50cloud.jpg\" alt=\"Sage 50Cloud\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233692\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sage-50cloud.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sage-50cloud-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sage-50cloud-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sage 50Cloud is another alternative to QuickBooks. You can connect Sage 50Cloud with your bank account to manage transactions, record sales, and generate real-time receipts. It has a custom panel to create, edit, and send invoices to your customers directly from the software. You can also send quotes to your clients in a professional style.</p>\n<p>This software helps manage your stocks and inventory. It takes care of tax calculation and automatically files returns online with HMRC service. Sage 50Cloud has many automation processes for accounting that makes it robust and unique.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs 20 per month. If you want to test the service, then you can sign up for their 30-day free trial.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://zipbooks.com/\" title=\"ZipBooks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. ZipBooks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://zipbooks.com/\" title=\"ZipBooks\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zipbooks.jpg\" alt=\"ZipBooks\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233693\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zipbooks.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zipbooks-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/zipbooks-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ZipBooks is a free accounting and online invoicing software. Like other popular solutions, it allows you to send professional invoices to clients and get paid instantly. It accepts all credit cards, PayPal, and other payment methods. You can also schedule payments and automate the billing process.</p>\n<p>It automatically categorizes the payments with color-coding to make it simpler and more accessible. With smart insights and reports, you can retain your high paying customers and boost the revenue.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a free version with all the features you need to compete with QuickBooks. ZipBooks also offer premium solutions starting from $15 / month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.freeagent.com\" title=\"FreeAgent\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. FreeAgent</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.freeagent.com\" title=\"FreeAgent\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freeagent.jpg\" alt=\"FreeAgent\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233694\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freeagent.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freeagent-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/freeagent-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>FreeAgent is an easy to use accounting software for small businesses and one of the best QuickBooks alternatives. It&#8217;s built for freelancers, individual website owners, and small agencies. It has impressive features like recurring invoices, automatic payment reminders, notifications, and more.</p>\n<p>It ships with a feature to snap the receipts and save them in your phone. FreeAgent connects with your bank to track the transactions and gives you a real-time view of your cash flow.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It starts at $10 per month for 6 months. Later, it costs $20 per month. You can sign up for their 30-day free trial to check all features before purchasing this solution.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.waveapps.com/\" title=\"Wave\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Wave</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.waveapps.com/\" title=\"Wave\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wave.jpg\" alt=\"Wave\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233695\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wave.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wave-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/wave-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Wave is a free financial software for small business websites. It helps you manage accounts, billing, and online invoices. With Wave, you can create beautiful invoices and send them to clients with a payment link for quick payments.</p>\n<p>It has a mobile app to manage all the transactions, save snaps of receipts, etc. It comes with a robust knowledge base that helps you guide you through setting up the accounting software.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It&#8217;s absolutely free. You can sign up on their website to get started.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://bench.co/\" title=\"Bench\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Bench</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://bench.co/\" title=\"Bench\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/bench.jpg\" alt=\"Bench\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233696\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/bench.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/bench-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/bench-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Bench is an excellent bookkeeping service for small business websites. It integrates with popular apps like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-up-shopify-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Set Up Shopify with WordPress (Step by Step)\">Shopify</a>, WordPress, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/bigcommerce-vs-woocommerce/\" title=\"BigCommerce vs WooCommerce: What Should You Choose?\">BigCommerce</a>, Stripe, etc. It gives you complete control over your income with monthly statements, expense overviews, and insights on your transactions.</p>\n<p>It offers a yearly financial package and makes it easy for you to file taxes manually. The Bench is one of the best alternatives to QuickBooks.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Its starting price is $119 per month when paid annually. You can take sign up for their free trial for testing the service.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.pandle.com\" title=\"Pandle\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Pandle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pandle.com\" title=\"Pandle\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pandle.jpg\" alt=\"Pandle\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233697\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pandle.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pandle-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/pandle-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Pandle is another free accounting software for small businesses. It presents your income and cash flow in graphical format. Similar to any premium accounting software, Pandle allows you to add the payment link to your invoice and get paid quickly. It smartly manages your finances by categorizing the transactions.</p>\n<p>With their mobile app, you can send quotes, invoices, and more. Pandle app improves the bookkeeping experience and helps you grow your business.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a free plan with amazing features. For more options, you can purchase their premium version at $7 per month.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://kashoo.com\" title=\"Kashoo\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Kashoo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://kashoo.com\" title=\"Kashoo\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/kashoo.jpg\" alt=\"Kashoo\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233698\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/kashoo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/kashoo-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/kashoo-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Kashoo is simple accounting software for small business owners. It has an easy-to-use dashboard to display your transactions in real-time. It reconciles the data of over 5000 bank feeds, making it easier for you to manage the cash flow.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s easy to set up and use. Kashoo allows you to send professional invoices to clients and is compatible with multiple payment gateways, including credit cards, PayPal, etc. </p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $19.95 per month if billed annually. Kashoo has a 14-day free trial to test the service.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://gusto.com\" title=\"Gusto\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Gusto</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://gusto.com\" title=\"Gusto\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gusto.jpg\" alt=\"Gusto\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233687\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gusto.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gusto-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/gusto-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Gusto is an online payroll service to manage your employees accounts professionally. It may not be a direct competitor to QuickBooks, but you can use it to run your business smoothly and settle payments on the go.</p>\n<p>It helps you collaborate with companies offering benefits for employees. You can use this service to automate in-house transactions easily.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It costs $12 / month per person. Gusto has a 30-day free trial.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find out the best QuickBooks alternatives to manage your accounts. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-email-accounts-for-your-domain-name/\" title=\"How to Create Email Accounts for Your Domain Name\">how to create email accounts for your business name</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/quickbooks-alternatives/\">11 Best QuickBooks Alternatives for Small Businesses (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:1