DN services for WordPress [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-cdn-services/\">10 Best CDN Services to Speed Up Your Website (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14196:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress CDN services?</p>\n<p>Content delivery networks (CDN) cache the content from your website on multiple servers in different geographical locations. It delivers the content to your site visitor through a server that is closest to them.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best CDN services for WordPress that can help you speed up your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/stackpath-cdn/\" title=\"StackPath CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. StackPath CDN</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/stackpath-cdn/\" title=\"StackPath CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/stackpath.jpg\" alt=\"StackPath\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233222\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/stackpath.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/stackpath-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/stackpath-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>StackPath is one of the best CDN services for WordPress websites. StackPath is previously known as MaxCDN. It has an intelligent caching system, instant purge mechanism, and custom cache rules to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/boost-wordpress-performance-speed/\" title=\"How to Boost WordPress Performance &#038; Speed (Expert Advice)\">boost your site performance</a>. StackPath CDN owns a vast network of servers in all continents.</p>\n<p>It comes with real-time analytics, custom EdgeRules, segmented downloads option, and serverless scripting feature. The basic plan can have up to 1 TB of monthly bandwidth.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> Its cost starts from $20 per month. The first-month service is free of cost.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/keycdn/\" title=\"KeyCDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. KeyCDN</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/keycdn/\" title=\"KeyCDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/keycdn.jpg\" alt=\"KeyCDN\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233225\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/keycdn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/keycdn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/keycdn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>KeyCDN is one of the most powerful content delivery networks that come with 34 data centers around the globe. You can install their WordPress plugin called CDN Enabler to easily integrate KeyCDN to your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>The best part is that the plugin allows you to purge your CDN Zones cache directly from your WordPress admin. This means you don&#8217;t have to log into the KeyCDN dashboard to purge the cache.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a pay-as-you-go policy and charges on the usage. KeyCDN offers a 30-day free trial.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. Sucuri</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sucuri.jpg\" alt=\"Sucuri\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233224\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sucuri.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sucuri-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/sucuri-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sucuri is the best <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/\" title=\"6 Best WordPress Security Plugins\">website security</a>, monitoring, and protection service. Aside from security, they also offer a CDN solution for performance and speed optimization of your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">WordPress site</a>. It features multiple caching options for all types of websites.</p>\n<p>Their CDN runs on the Anycast network with the global distribution of servers. The configuration for Sucuri CDN has custom options to maximize the website speed.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/sucuri/\" title=\"Sucuri Review: Why We Love Sucuri + Pros and Cons\">Sucuri review</a> for more information about their services.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The basic plan costs $199.99 per year.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\" title=\"Cloudflare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Cloudflare</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/\" title=\"Cloudflare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cloudflare.jpg\" alt=\"Cloudflare\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233223\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cloudflare.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cloudflare-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cloudflare-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Cloudflare is an excellent web performance and security service. It has the largest cloud network platform with 180 data centers around the world and has been securing over 16 million domains. You can use it to accelerate your web pages, mobile applications, and APIs. </p>\n<p>It offers a free plugin and drastically improves the performance of WordPress sites with minimal configuration. It also defends your website from DDoS attacks and malicious content.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The pro plan starts from $20 per month. They also offer a free account with basic features.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cloudfront/\" title=\"Amazon CloudFront\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Amazon CloudFront</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cloudfront/\" title=\"Amazon CloudFront\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-cloudfront.jpg\" alt=\"Amazon CloudFront\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233226\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-cloudfront.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-cloudfront-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/amazon-cloudfront-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Amazon CloudFront is an AWS integrated CDN service that delivers your website content to your visitors instantly. The AWS network boosts CDN with their other services and offers high transfer speed all over the world. It&#8217;s an advanced service for developers and programmers.</p>\n<p>That being said, you&#8217;ll have to tackle a slight learning curve to set up Amazon CloudFront.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It has a pay-as-you-go model and charges only for the service you use. With AWS, you&#8217;ll also get free trials for a short period.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.cachefly.com/\" title=\"CacheFly\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. CacheFly</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cachefly.com/\" title=\"CacheFly\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cachefly.jpg\" alt=\"CacheFly\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233227\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cachefly.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cachefly-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/cachefly-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>CacheFly is one of the oldest content delivery networks on the market. Based on Anycast network, they help you improve your website speed and delivers the content swiftly. This CDN service stream videos and podcasts with lightning fast speed.</p>\n<p>Whenever you need assistance, you can get in touch with their excellent support team that can answer your pertinent questions regarding CDN. </p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> The starting cost for small business plans is $245 per month paid annually. On a prepay, you&#8217;ll also get 2 months of free service. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.rackspace.com/\" title=\"Rackspace\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Rackspace</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.rackspace.com/\" title=\"Rackspace\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/rackspace.jpg\" alt=\"Rackspace\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233228\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/rackspace.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/rackspace-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/rackspace-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Rackspace is a premium cloud computing service that uses the Akamai&#8217;s network and streams the content up to 200 locations around the globe.</p>\n<p>It supports eCommerce stores, WordPress websites, web applications, mobile applications, and more. It&#8217;s a bit tech-savvy service and needs advanced knowledge to set up.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It is a pay-as-you-go service so you can only pay for the bandwidth you consume. The service is fully scalable to handle any traffic load.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/cdn/\" title=\"Google Cloud CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Google Cloud CDN</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/cdn/\" title=\"Google Cloud CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/google-cloud-cdn.jpg\" alt=\"Google Cloud CDN\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233229\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/google-cloud-cdn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/google-cloud-cdn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/google-cloud-cdn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Cloud CDN is a low-cost content delivery network service. With 90 servers around the globe, it has the fastest content delivery to your users on any location. It comes with quick page loads and increases user engagement on your website. Google Cloud CDN provides a single IP address to all your users and needs no regional DNS.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s packed with free SSL to make your website secure. It&#8217;s integrated with Google Cloud Platform and you can enable CDN with a single checkbox.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> You need to sign up for the Google Cloud Platform to get access to CDN. The cost for Google Cloud Platform is based on your usage.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-in/services/cdn/\" title=\"Microsoft Azure CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Microsoft Azure CDN</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-in/services/cdn/\" title=\"Microsoft Azure CDN\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/microsoft-azure-cdn.jpg\" alt=\"Microsoft Azure CDN\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233230\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/microsoft-azure-cdn.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/microsoft-azure-cdn-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/microsoft-azure-cdn-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a secure and reliable content delivery network, then Microsoft Azure CDN is a perfect choice. It has global coverage and massive scalability for content delivery. It integrates with all the Azure services that make CDN solution more useful.</p>\n<p>Azure CDN reduces the page load time, saves bandwidth, and speed up the web pages. It works great with websites, apps, and gaming software.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> It works on the pay-as-you-go model.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.imperva.com/products/cdn-content-delivery-network/\" title=\"Imperva\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Imperva</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.imperva.com/products/cdn-content-delivery-network/\" title=\"Imperva\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/imperva.jpg\" alt=\"Imperva\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233221\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/imperva.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/imperva-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/imperva-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Imperva is one of the best CDN services that use intelligent caching, high-speed storage, and optimization tools. It comes with advanced machine learning technology for dynamic caching. You can instantly purge cache and has custom cache control options.</p>\n<p>The data centers are strategically placed in all regions around the globe to serve the content from a server that&#8217;s closer to the users. Imperva optimizes the content, automate compression, and do a lot more like premium a CDN service.</p>\n<p><strong>Price:</strong> You need to request for a quote.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s all.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best CDN services for your WordPress website. You may also want to check out our step by step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-cdn-services/\">10 Best CDN Services to Speed Up Your Website (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-cdn-services/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0: