\"<p>Are you looking for a discount wheel popup plugin? A discount wheel or a spin-a-wheel popup is an optin form that encourages your site visitors to take action quickly. Thus, it helps you build your email list and boost product sales.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll compare the best WordPress spinning wheel popup plugins and help you to choose the right one for your needs.</p>\n<h3>Why You Should Use Discount Wheel Popups?</h3>\n<p>You&#8217;re already using popups and subscription boxes on your site to collect emails from your visitors. Then what&#8217;s the point of using a discount wheel popup?</p>\n<p>A discount wheel popup uses<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/gamification-in-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">gamification technique</a> to increase the engagement of your site visitors.</p>\n<p>When your visitors see a spin-a-wheel game popup, it sparks curiosity among them and challenges them to interact or play with it. It also acts as a sense of achievement for them to win something.</p>\n<p>Hence, you can use it to provide different incentives to your site visitors to<a href=\"http://optinmonster.com/beginners-guide-to-email-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">grow your email list</a> or increase the sales of your product.</p>\n<p>Thanks to WordPress, you can easily add a spinning wheel popup to your website with the help of a plugin.</p>\n<p>So without further ado, let&#8217;s take a look at the best discount wheel popup plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">1. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506373\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-best-wheel-discount-popup-plugin.png\" alt=\"OptinMonster best wheel discount popup plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"572\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-best-wheel-discount-popup-plugin.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-best-wheel-discount-popup-plugin-300x154.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-best-wheel-discount-popup-plugin-768x394.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-best-wheel-discount-popup-plugin-1024x525.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful lead generation software in the market. It helps you build your email list, generate more leads, and increase your product sales.</p>\n<p>One of the features of this amazing tool is the ability to add spin-a-wheel popups to your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>You can use it to offer incentives like discounts, gifts, ebooks, and more. This will help you to easily <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/11-ways-to-increase-conversion-rates-on-your-thank-you-pages/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">increase the conversion rates</a> as people love to play games and win exciting prizes.</p>\n<p>In the process, you can grow your email list by connecting the popup form to your email marketing software.</p>\n<p>And the good news is OptinMonster can be integrated with almost every service including <a title=\"Constant Contact\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Constant Contact</a>, <a title=\"AWeber\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/aweber-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">AWeber</a>, <a title=\"MailChimp\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/mailchimp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">MailChimp</a>, <a title=\"ConvertKit\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/refer/convertkit/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ConvertKit</a>, and more.</p>\n<p>This plugin also lets you customize the discount wheel popupusing the easy-to-use drag and drop builder.</p>\n<p>You can start designing the popup using any of the 3 ready-to-use templates. You can even add different colors to match the popup with your brand colors.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s an example of a discount wheel popup:</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506375\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-spin-a-wheel-example.png\" alt=\"optinmonster spin-a-wheel example\" width=\"1116\" height=\"557\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-spin-a-wheel-example.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-spin-a-wheel-example-300x150.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-spin-a-wheel-example-768x383.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinmonster-spin-a-wheel-example-1024x511.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Not only that but you can also edit the wheel sections and pick the prize for each of them.</p>\n<p>So what are you waiting for? <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get started with OptinMonster today</a>!</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-optin-wheel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">2. WP Optin Wheel</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506387\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wp-optin-wheel-plugin.png\" alt=\"WP Optin Wheel plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wp-optin-wheel-plugin.png 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wp-optin-wheel-plugin-300x139.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>WP Optin Wheel is a freemium gamification plugin for WordPress and WooCommerce. It gives you total control over the wheel popup, so you can easily customize it the way you want.</p>\n<p>You can even create multiple wheels for different campaigns without much hassle. Also, you can control when you want to show the popup to your visitors.</p>\n<p>Just like OptinMonster, this plugin allows you to set up each of the 12 sections of the wheel. You can decide what you should offer to your prospective customers and then display it on the wheel easily.</p>\n<p>WP Optin Wheel is a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-add-a-gdpr-agreement-field-to-your-sites-forms/\">GDPR-ready</a> plugin, so you can get consent from your website visitors before collecting their information.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woo-lucky-wheel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">3. Lucky Wheel for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506383\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/lucky-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Lucky Wheel for WooCommerce plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"181\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/lucky-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin.jpg 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/lucky-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin-300x97.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Lucky Wheel for WooCommerce is a spin-a-wheel plugin for online stores. You can use it to build your email list by asking your visitors to play the wheel game.</p>\n<p>You can decide whether the popup will open up automatically or it&#8217;ll appear by clicking on a small wheel icon, present at the corner of the screen.</p>\n<p>Some of the amazing features of this plugin are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Limit the spinning times for each user</li>\n<li>6 different popup positions to choose from</li>\n<li>Configure the winning probability of each section of the wheel in percentages</li>\n<li>Send coupon code to the winners via email</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Apart from the above, Lucky Wheel plugin also allows you to use <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/ultimate-guide-wordpress-conditional-tags/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WordPress conditional tags</a> to set up the pages on which the popup should appear.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/optin-spin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">4. OptinSpin</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506384\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinspin-wordpress-plugin.png\" alt=\"OptinSpin WordPress plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinspin-wordpress-plugin.png 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/optinspin-wordpress-plugin-300x139.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>OptinSpin is a fully customizable spinning wheel popup plugin. It&#8217;s compatible with popular plugins like Easy Digital Downloads and WooCommerce.</p>\n<p>You can easily integrate it to the WooCommerce Coupons plugin to create coupons and send it to your site visitors automatically.</p>\n<p>Just like most plugins on our list, you&#8217;ll be able to change the color of each section of the wheel. Plus, you can add your business logo to the wheel to promote your brand.</p>\n<p>You can also upgrade to the premium version of this plugin to get additional benefits. You&#8217;ll get extra features like time delay, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-install-and-use-zapier-addon-with-wpforms/\">Zapier integration</a>, set probability for each section, customize email templates, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://makewebbetter.com/product/discount-win-wheel-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Discount Win-Wheel for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506372\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/discount-win-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin.png\" alt=\"Discount Win-Wheel for WooCommerce plugin\" width=\"1116\" height=\"557\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/discount-win-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin.png 1116w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/discount-win-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin-300x150.png 300w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/discount-win-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin-768x383.png 768w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/discount-win-wheel-for-woocommerce-plugin-1024x511.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1116px) 100vw, 1116px\" /></p>\n<p>Discount Win-Wheel for WooCommerce is a premium and mobile-friendly plugin. It&#8217;ll help you to boost the engagement of your site visitors so that you can increase the sales of your product.</p>\n<p>It comes with a <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-drag-and-drop-wordpress-page-builders/\">drag and drop builder</a> to change the position of the wheel sections. You can also add or remove the sections based on your needs.</p>\n<p>One of the features that need special mention is the ability to generate coupon codes dynamically. You can also track the coupon status from your WordPress admin panel.</p>\n<p>The Discount Win-Wheel for WooCommerce plugin also comes with useful features like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Offers multiple triggers like on page load, on icon click, and on exit.</li>\n<li>Set up the popup display timing easily</li>\n<li>Ability to add the popup wheel on multiple locations</li>\n<li>Compatible with the WPML plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/crazyrocket-pop-ups/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. Wheel by CrazyRocket</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506385\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheel-by-crazyrocket-plugin.png\" alt=\"Wheel by CrazyRocket plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"249\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheel-by-crazyrocket-plugin.png 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheel-by-crazyrocket-plugin-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>Wheel by CrazyRocket is a relatively newer plugin compared to the rest. However, it offers some amazing features to increase your conversion rate.</p>\n<p>It comes with some beautifully designed popup templates to choose from. And you can easily customize the popup the way you want.</p>\n<p>Apart from the spinning wheel feature, this plugin offers 2 exciting popup games: scratch card and slot machine. You can use these games to generate curiosity among your visitors and encourage them to take action.</p>\n<p>Some of the other features of this plugin are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use a countdown timer in your popup</li>\n<li>GDPR (<a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/the-ultimate-guide-to-wordpress-and-gdpr-compliance-everything-you-need-to-know/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">General Data Protection Regulation</a>) compliant</li>\n<li>Offers <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">easy to understand analytics</a></li>\n<li>Generate unique coupons automatically</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/lucky-wheel-exit-intent-wheelio-popup-for-spin-a-sale-by-wheely-sales/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">7. Wheely Sales</a></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-506386\" src=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheely-sales-plugin.png\" alt=\"Wheely Sales plugin\" width=\"558\" height=\"181\" srcset=\"https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheely-sales-plugin.png 558w, https://wpforms.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wheely-sales-plugin-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /></p>\n<p>Wheely Sales is a premium spin-a-wheel plugin for WordPress. It&#8217;s responsive to every screen size, so your popups will look beautiful on mobiles, tablets, and desktops.</p>\n<p>This plugin allows you to customize the popups easily. You can change colors, add your business logo, and specify the prizes your visitors can win.</p>\n<p>The Wheely Sales plugin can be integrated with MailChimp to collect emails from your visitors. You can also use Zapier to connect this plugin to any app or <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/showcase/best-email-marketing-services/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">email marketing service</a>.</p>\n<h3>Which Plugin is the Best For Your Needs?</h3>\n<p>After comparing the above plugins, we can easily conclude that <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is the best discount wheel popup plugin for WordPress. It helps you design the popups easily and also supports almost every email marketing service.</p>\n<p>However, you should remember that OptinMonster is not just a spin-a-wheel plugin. It&#8217;s the most powerful lead generation tool that allows you to create different types of forms including floating bars, fullscreen overlays, and slide-ins.</p>\n<p>It also offers features like 75+ pre-made templates, A/B testing, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/exit-intent-popup-examples/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Exit Intent<sup></sup></a>, advanced traffic redirection, page level targeting, and much more.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to select the best discount wheel popup plugin for your website.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, then you may also want to check out our step by step tutorial on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-create-a-contact-form-popup-in-wordpress/\">how to create a contact form popup in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, please follow us on <a href=\"http://facebook.com/wpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> and <a href=\"http://twitter.com/easywpforms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> to get updates from our blog.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-discount-wheel-popup-plugins/\">7 Best Discount Wheel Popup Plugins for WordPress (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpforms.com\">WPForms</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s: